OL,3,CPatients told to stay away after major
OL,4,Cfire at hospital
OL,6,FPatients are being told to stay away
OL,7,Ffrom a North Yorkshire hospital
OL,8,Ffollowing a major fire.
OL,10,FThe fire broke out in the Springwood
OL,11,Funit, which provides mental health
OL,12,Fservices for older people, at Malton
OL,13,Fand Norton District Hospital on
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,16,FPatients and staff were led to safety
OL,17,Fand no-one was injured.
OL,19,FHumber Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,20,Fsaid all patients had been relocated.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
