OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1783703991
OL,3,CPatients told to stay away after major
OL,4,Cfire at hospital
OL,6,FThe NHS trust said in a statement: "We
OL,7,Fask patients not to attend the
OL,8,Fhospital at this time.
OL,10,F"Patients with affected appointments
OL,11,Fwill be contacted directly as soon as
OL,12,Fpossible to rearrange or advise on the
OL,13,Fnext steps.
OL,15,F"The safety of our patients, visitors
OL,16,Fand colleagues remains our absolute
OL,17,Fpriority. We would like to thank our
OL,18,Fstaff, the emergency services and
OL,19,Fpartner organisations for their swift
OL,20,Fresponse and support."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
