PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1783703991
OL,3,CPatients told to stay away after major
OL,4,Cfire at hospital
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService said crews worked through the
OL,8,Fnight on Wednesday to extinguish the
OL,9,Ffire and checked for hotspots.
OL,11,FOne fire engine remained on the scene
OL,12,Fon Thursday. The cause of the blaze
OL,13,Fhas not yet been established.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
